 .../crash-memory-driver_8.0.6.bb              | 42 ++++++++++++++
 ...01-hacked-Makefilefor-module.bbclass.patch | 57 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../files/0002-add-sparse-support.patch       | 30 ++++++++++
